# Thread Priority

Priority ranges from **1 to 10**.

| Constant      | Value |
| ------------- | ----- |
| MIN_PRIORITY  | 1     |
| NORM_PRIORITY | 5     |
| MAX_PRIORITY  | 10    |

Example:

```java
Thread t1 = new Thread();

t1.setPriority(Thread.MAX_PRIORITY);
```

